    "description": "Are you a skilled Full Stack Developer looking for your next big career move? Cisco India South Asia Partners in Kolkata offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Cisco India South Asia Partners:\nCisco India South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kolkata, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Cisco India South Asia Partners!",
